doctype html
html
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        title Password Reset - SaveOurVotes
    body(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;")
        div(style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;")
            h2 Password Reset Request

            p Hi #{fullName},

            p You requested to reset your password. Click the link below to reset it:

            p
                a(href=url style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;") Reset Password

            p(style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;")
                | Or copy this link: 
                br
                = url

            p(style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;")
                | This link will expire in 10 minutes.

            hr

            p(style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;")
                | If you didn't request this, please ignore this email or 
                a(href="mailto:" + supportEmail) contact us.

            p(style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;")
                | Â© SaveOurVotes. All rights reserved.
